leadership-approach|results_process_people_vision|strength_3|3|Range through wider direction after People|People can broaden the first two signals before Vision is brought in deliberately. Vision adds range when the pattern is handling people, structure, or delivery and now needs a stronger reason for the work. It can lift the decision from the immediate task to meaning and future consequence.|vision|active|leadership-approach::results_process_people_vision::strength_3
leadership-approach|results_vision_process_people|strength_1|1|Clear movement|When this pattern is working well, Results gives leadership a clear line of movement. Decisions, owners, and next steps are easier to see, so the work is less likely to sit in drift or unresolved discussion.|results|active|leadership-approach::results_vision_process_people::strength_1
leadership-approach|results_vision_process_people|strength_2|2|Progress with direction|Results and Vision together can connect action to a bigger reason. The strength is that decisions are not only made; they are tied to a direction people can understand beyond the immediate task.|vision|active|leadership-approach::results_vision_process_people::strength_2
leadership-approach|results_vision_process_people|strength_3|3|Range through stronger trust after Process|Process can broaden the first two signals before People is brought in deliberately. People adds range when the pattern has movement, structure, or direction and now needs better communication around the human impact. It can make progress more sustainable because people understand their part in the work.|people|active|leadership-approach::results_vision_process_people::strength_3
