leadership-approach|results_vision_people_process|strength_3|3|Range through clearer structure after People|People can broaden the first two signals before Process is brought in deliberately. Process adds range when the pattern has energy, meaning, or commitment and now needs a more dependable way to hold the work. It can turn shared intent into steps, standards, and cleaner handover.|process|active|leadership-approach::results_vision_people_process::strength_3
